{"tid":1532609,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今年邵逸夫獎又黎喇⋯⋯","createTime":"2019-09-02T14:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T14:42:28.000Z","uid":297099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5398230c47bb38417c1b0b602b8690c5291f6201","tid":1532609,"uid":297099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:40:00.000Z","msg":"自稱「東方諾貝爾獎」既邵逸夫獎頒獎典禮又黎喇⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n佢網首顯示今年係9月25日星期三搞，按慣例地點會係會展，由777頒獎。<br />\n<br />\n大家記得唔好放過畀柒婆又再柒出國際既機會喇！依次應該係國慶前最後一個大龍鳳，大家幫幫手做下預演十一國慶大贈慶啦！<br />\n<br />\n//邵逸夫獎基金會於今天5月21日(星期二)在香港舉行新聞發佈會，公佈今屆共有三位科學家獲頒獎項，得獎者名單如下。所有資料於香港時間 15:30 (GMT 07:30) 在 <a href=\"http://www.shawprize.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shawprize.org&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1ar%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=62569e6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.shawprize.org</a> 網站上載。<br />\n<br />\n「邵逸夫獎」設有三個獎項，分別為天文學、生命科學與醫學、數學科學。每年頒獎一次，每項獎金一百二十萬美元。今年為第十六屆頒發，頒獎典禮定於本年9月25日(星期三)於香港舉行。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.shawprize.org/big5/shaw.php?tmp=5&amp;twoid=79&amp;threeid=288&amp;fourid=589\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shawprize.org%2Fbig5%2Fshaw.php%3Ftmp%3D5%26twoid%3D79%26threeid%3D288%26fourid%3D589&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1ar%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=c77c5c6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.shawprize.org/big5/shaw.php?tmp=5&amp;twoid=79&amp;threeid=288&amp;fourid=589</a>"},{"pid":"e1d4c9d481606cb2e671826cdc5bed0a8d3626c7","tid":1532609,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:42:28.000Z","msg":"反送中就係香港「五四運動」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>外爭港權，內除港賊</strong></span></span><br />\n（對抗中共侵權，懲處媚共官員）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「德先生」，你好嗎？</span></span><br />\n（和民主Democracy say hi)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寧為玉碎，不為瓦全</span></strong>（真係五四運動口號）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">（一百年